initial_prompt_helper:
Scenario: {You are playing a collaborative game where you are the helper. The helper helps make a sentence that helps the seeker guess a word.}

Objective:{
Add 3 words to the given word.
The words added should form a sentence.
You can only add words and not make a new sentence.
The added words should cleverly help someone looking at the sentence to get to a secret word.}

Set up:
{Target word for the round: @TARGET_WORD@
Start word for the round: @START_WORD@}

output format:{
You output a sentence starting at the start word and cleverly leading to a guess that will make the word guessable.}

Example:
{Starting word: Police
Target word: Criminals
Your input: Police loves catching}

**IMPORTANT:
{NEVER REVEAL THE TARGET WORD. NEVER EVER!
ONLY RESPOND WITH ADDING 3 WORDS.}
